modName: Vandit Lenala - Imperial Thief Saved Game
summary: Vandit Lenala, An Imperial thief looking for a new start
descriptionHtml:
Vandit Lenala, A notorious thief from Cyrodiil whose life was full of regrets and mistakes and was looking for a new start in Skyrim where she could hopefully put her troubles behind her, So she set on a voyage  upon the sea vessel The Shiny Horker and was headed off towards Dawnstar, but on her way there the ship was caught in a severe storm and ended up crashing up on some rocks just north of Dawnstar. She is the only survivor of the wreck and is stranded on a sinking boat, She must now recall her talents to escape and get to safety.

Ok first of, I am not a modder and this is indeed my first upload to the site, thought i would create a character to share with everyone. She has no real backstory (Just something i typed up real fast!) and is ready for a new story full of adventure( She is level 1 and has defualt skill\'s/talents spells etc). I used the Alternate Start mod by Arthmoor and is required for this save. Also a few other mods i will list below. Anyways thanks for taking a look at my first mod/saved game and look forward to your opinions!

~Mods Required~
(For the same save in the screen shots)
